## Sample Queries

### Students with CGPA Greater Than 3.5

```sql
SELECT *
FROM Student
WHERE student_cgpa > 3.5;
```

### Department-wise Student Count

```sql
SELECT dep_Name, COUNT(*)
FROM Student
JOIN Department
ON Student.dep_ID = Department.dep_ID
GROUP BY dep_Name;
```

### Students Above Average CGPA

```sql
SELECT *
FROM Student
WHERE student_cgpa >
(
    SELECT AVG(student_cgpa)
    FROM Student
);
```

### Highest CGPA Student

```sql
SELECT *
FROM Student
ORDER BY student_cgpa DESC
LIMIT 1;
```

