## View Implementation

### Student Report View

```sql
CREATE VIEW Student_Report AS
SELECT s.student_id,
       s.student_name,
       d.dep_Name,
       s.student_cgpa
FROM Student s
JOIN Department d
ON s.dep_ID = d.dep_ID;
```

This view provides a simplified report containing student details along with their department information.

